Okay, I’ve always wanted to make this post but i was too lazy, i knoooww that was a stupid excuse. Okay so here it is. 
I WAS...
body:
Freddie is Brianna’s brother

Okay, I’ve always wanted to make this post but i was too lazy, i knoooww that was a stupid excuse. Okay so here it is.

I WAS ONLY MONTHS NEW in the Larry fandom when i did this digging. I was so frustrated when I saw that Freddie was growing up into a mini Louis! The kid is sooo cute, but Im too skeptical for him to be Louis’ son. Like what? Lou’s gonna cheat on Harry like that? Oh no… if youre a Larrie and think that is lou’s kid, then you dont know their love. Here is Freddie, sucha cute kid:

Now, isnt he cute?? Looks A LOT like Louis, right? Like if Louis’ walking around with him people are instantly gonna assume he’s his kid. I mean look at the eyes, the brows, and the nose! Even CHOP SUEY’S EYELASHES! But then… I saw Brianna’s brother (stepbrother I believe) that’s supposed to be Freddie’s uncle.

The one on the left, this was posted on instagram by the way. Now look again and notice the eyes, nose, lips, FACE. You dont even have to look closely to notice that they look alike. He looks like Freddie, alot. But then, he looks like Louis too😂

So here’s a picture of our sweet baby Louis and Lottie.


I MUST SAY, MODEST WAS REALLY GOOD FINDING A LOUIS LOOKALIKE. but we caught them 🧐

summary: I kinda disappeared not gonna lie. I’ve been going through some creative blocks due to some personal emotional/mental issues but...
body:
I kinda disappeared not gonna lie. I’ve been going through some creative blocks due to some personal emotional/mental issues but finally was able to come up with something small. I didn’t edit much but I was just excited to finally put something else out there. This also doesn’t have a title. I’m planning to be a lot more active so please share and submit any requests of what you’d like to see! xoxo -Ellie

“I don’t know what I’m feeling!” She lets out an exasperated sigh. “I try so hard to just come up with a reason why and I just-” Her voice breaks at the end. Her eyes begin to pool up with unshed tears. “I just don’t know, all I know is it doesn’t feel good.” She chokes out. She brings her knees to her chest hugging them close. She presses her forehead against her knees refusing to let him see the tears fall.

“I’ve told you love, please don’t hide from me.” He finally sits down close to her gently tugging at her left hand. “Your pain is my pain.” She releases a quiet ‘I know’ as sobs rack through her whole chest. A feeling so tight her breathing was coming out very shallow. He had never experienced a panic attack with her, he knew she had a history of them but this was the first time she had one around him.

“Hey, hey I’m right here. I’m right here.” He tries to remain calm to not heighten her anxiety.

“Remember the breathing techniques. Inhale four, hold seven, release eight” He says stepping away so as to not make her feel even more confined. “I’ll run and get you water but please breather for me.” He starts to make his way towards the door when he hears a breathy ‘wait’. He turns and walks back to her maintaining a bit of distance. She holds out her hand for him silently waiting for him to take it.

“Please don’t leave me.” She whispers shakily as she continues with her 4-7-8 breathing. He takes hold of her hand placing himself at her feet, breathing along with her. They stay like this for a few minutes sitting in silence waiting for her to finally catch her breath. Her eyes are rimmed red and glossy and she sits unmoving. Harry makes a move to stand but her hold tightens.

“I’m just gonna bring you some water, petal. I’ll be quick” he says in a soft voice. She lets go and hugs her knees to her chest again placing her cheek on them. She rubs at her eyes to clear her face of the few straying tears. Harry returns with a glass half filled and places it on the nightstand next to her. He places himself by her feet being cautious of not startling her.

“I think I need to see a professional” she mumbles still looking away sniffling here and there. He passes the box of tissues toward her.

“Whatever you need to do, I’ll be there every step of the way with you.” He responds gently stroking the back of her hand. She sniffs again adjusting her position to sit closer to him wrapping her arms around his torso and laying her head on his shoulder. Some stubborn tears still falling. He strokes her hair placing a few soft kisses on her head. She may not have known what was going on in her head, but one thing she was sure of was the love she had for this boy.

“I think I need to see a professional” she mumbles still looking away sniffling here and there. He passes the box of tissues toward her.

“Whatever you need to do, I’ll be there every step of the way with you.” He responds gently stroking the back of her hand. She sniffs again adjusting her position to sit closer to him wrapping her arms around his torso and laying her head on his shoulder. Some stubborn tears still falling. He strokes her hair placing a few soft kisses on her head. She may not have known what was going on in her head, but one thing she was sure of was the love she had for this boy.

“I’ve told you love, please don’t hide from me.” He finally sits down close to her gently tugging at her left hand. “Your pain is my pain.” She releases a quiet ‘I know’ as sobs rack through her whole chest.
